.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It ECHO
Copies
.Fa yytext
to the scanner's output.
.It BEGIN
Followed by the name of a start condition, places the scanner in the
corresponding start condition
.Pq see below .
.It REJECT
Directs the scanner to proceed on to the
