.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "<g++/FlexLexer.h>"
.It flex.skl
Skeleton scanner.
This file is only used when building flex, not when
.Nm
executes.
.It lex.backup
Backing-up information for the
.Fl b
flag (called
.Pa lex.bck
on some systems).
.It lex.yy.c
Generated scanner
(called
.Pa lexyy.c
on some systems).
.It lex.yy.cc
Generated C++ scanner class, when using
.Fl + .
.It Aq g++/FlexLexer.h
Header file defining the C++ scanner base class,
.Fa FlexLexer ,
and its derived class,
.Fa yyFlexLexer .
.It /usr/lib/libl.*
.Nm
libraries.
The
.Pa /usr/lib/libfl.*\&
libraries are links to these.
Scanners must be linked using either
.Fl \&ll
or
.Fl lfl .
